@wp.kernel
def compound_rwgc(a: wp.array(dtype=float), b: wp.array(dtype=float), c: wp.array(dtype=float), scale: float):
    tid = wp.tid()
    x = a[tid]
    y = b[tid]
    result = (x + y) * scale
    result = result - wp.floor(result)
    c[tid] = wp.abs(result)
